<h1 id="escapes">ESCAPES</h1>
<p>Color changes and fills carry no text.</p>
<p>A font family name and a register and an environment value are
dropped.</p>
<p>A macro string leaves nothing, a break and a leader vanish, and a
named glyph \ resolves.</p>
